	<div class="wide_post">
		<div class="post">
			<h1>OSP + Scribus = Prizewinning Design!</h1>
			<p class="meta"><a href="http://ospublish.constantvzw.org/category/news" title="View all posts in News" rel="category tag">News</a> &middot; June 5th, 2009 &middot;  <a href="http://ospublish.constantvzw.org/author/osp/" title="Posts by OSP">OSP</a></p>
			<div class="entry">
				<p><a href="http://gallery.constantvzw.org/main.php?g2_itemId=26159&#038;g2_page=2"><img src="http://ospublish.constantvzw.org/wp-content/uploads/dsc03255-400x300.jpg" alt="dsc03255" title="dsc03255" width="400" height="300" class="alignright size-medium wp-image-2891" /></a></p>
<p>Yesterday OSP received a <a href="http://www.plantinmoretusprijzen.be/?p=deprijs">Plantin-Moretus prize 2009</a> for best designed book in the category non fiction. The jury about <a href="http://www.lannoo.be/Content/lannoo/wbnl/listview/1/index.jsp?titelcode=14298&#038;fondsid=16">Cross-over</a>: &#8220;<em>It was love at first sight</em>&#8220;. The book, published by BAM and Lannoo and edited by Liesbeth Huybregts, uses Libre Fonts and is produced with Scribus and many other F/LOSS tools. We think it is probably the first publication made in Free Software crowned &#8216;best designed book&#8217; and we are sure it is not going to be the last!</p>
<p>The prize is named after <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Plantin-Moretus_Museum">Plantin Moretus</a>, a 16th century printing and publishing house in Antwerp renowned for its high quality cartography, typography and engraving.</p>
<p>OSP feels honoured <img src='http://ospublish.constantvzw.org/wp-includes/images/smilies/icon_smile.gif' alt=':-)' class='wp-smiley' />  </p>
<p>[<a href="http://gallery.constantvzw.org/main.php?g2_itemId=26159">more pictures</a>]</p>
							</div>
			<p class="meta">Tags:  &middot; <a href="http://ospublish.constantvzw.org/tag/awards" rel="tag">Awards</a>, <a href="http://ospublish.constantvzw.org/tag/libre-fonts" rel="tag">Libre Fonts</a>, <a href="http://ospublish.constantvzw.org/tag/printing-publishing" rel="tag">Printing + Publishing</a>, <a href="http://ospublish.constantvzw.org/tag/scribus" rel="tag">Scribus</a></p>
		</div>
			<div class="clear"></div>
		
